rows.label: qst006502_msg0001
rows.name:
You're Janiki, right? Give
back the treasure that
you stole from Jamin!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0002
rows.name: What's your problem, old lady?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0003
rows.name: O...old lady...?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't you pay him any
mind. He's only a brat.

rows.label: qst006502_msg0005
rows.name:
Shaddup, you big creep! I hope
all your hair falls out!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0006
rows.name:
Why, you little... Who d'you
think you're calling a creep?!
Oh, you're so in for it now!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0007
rows.name:
ANYWAY! Stealing from
people is bad! Do you want
to be a common thief?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0008
rows.name: Shaddup!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0009
rows.name:
If you're really not going to give
it back, you leave me no choice.

rows.label: qst006502_msg0010
rows.name:
I will be forced to unleash
my Eye of Shining Justice!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0011
rows.name: Say what?

rows.label: qst006502_msg0012
rows.name: E...Eye of Shining what?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0013
rows.name:
If I remove this eyepatch, my divine
eye will seek out any bad little boys
and seal them away, never to return!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0014
rows.name:
H-hah! As if I'm going to believe
a ridiculous lie like that!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0015
rows.name:
If you're so sure I'm lying,
shall we find out? You may
not live to regret it...

rows.label: qst006502_msg0016
rows.name:
A...all right, fine! I'll give
them back! You satisfied?!

rows.label: qst006502_msg0017
rows.name:
Now don't go stealing from
people any more, do you hear?

rows.label: qst006502_msg0018
rows.name:
The Eye of Shining Justice
always knows where to find you.

rows.label: qst006502_msg0019
rows.name:
All right, already... I won't
steal stuff, I promise...

rows.label: qst006502_msg0020
rows.name:
Damn. Your Eye of Shining Justice
is even cooler than mine...
